summary: AN ORDINANCE approving and confirming the final plat of "Valley Ridge", a replat of portions of Tracts 26 and 27, Sunnyside five Acre Tracts, as recorded in Volume 2 of Plats, page 120, records of King County, Washington, in Section 22, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., Seattle, King County, Washington (C.F. 287027).
